h of room for apps, pictures, and videos. Regretfully, there\'s no way to increase storage.</p><h3 style=\"margin-bottom: 5px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; line-height: 24px;\">Camera</h3><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(1, 19, 45); line-height: 26px;\">On the back of the iPhone 15 Pro is a 48MP Main camera with several complex capabilities, a 12MP Ultra Wide camera with a wide field of vision, and a 12MP Telephoto camera with 3x optical zoom in, 2x optical zoom out, and up to 15x digital zoom. These cameras include several capabilities, including as Night mode, ProRAW compatibility, and 4K video recording at up to 60 frames per second with HDR. The Sapphire crystal lens cover, as well as important software enhancements like Deep Fusion and Smart HDR 5, deliver remarkable photography results. The TrueDepth front camera, which has a 12MP resolution and an f/1.9 aperture, enables Animoji, Memoji, Night mode, and 4K video recording at up to 60 frames per second.</p><h3 style=\"margin-bottom: 5px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; line-height: 24px;\">Network &amp; Connectivity</h3><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(1, 19, 45); line-height: 26px;\">It iPhone 15 Pro features a 5G connection (sub-6 GHz), Gigabit LTE, Wi-Fi 6E (802.11ax), Bluetooth 5.3, and Precision dual-frequency GPS for exact position monitoring. It contains NFC capability with reader mode as well as a USB-C port for charging and data transmission.</p><h3 style=\"margin-bottom: 5px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; line-height: 24px;\">Operating System</h3><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(1, 19, 45); line-height: 26px;\">Replace it. Stick with iOS 17. The iPhone 15 Pro has Apple\'s most modern software features and innovations. iOS 17 contains new features to enhance the activities you undertake every day. When you call or text someone, express yourself like you\'ve never done before. Share information in more convenient ways. Do even more with new iPhone experiences.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(1, 19, 45); line-height: 26px;\"><span style=\"color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 21px;\">Gigablast your gigabits</span><br></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(1, 19, 45); line-height: 26px;\">The iPhone 15 Pro is the first iPhone to use USB 3, enabling faster data transfer speeds and professional workflows than ever before. File transfers can be 20 times faster. You can charge your Mac or iPad with the same cable that you use to power your iPhone 15 Pro thanks to the new USBC connector. Goodbye, cable tangle. The new WiFi 6E gives up to twice the wireless speed. As a result, you may upload and download files swiftly. Want to make a friend in a crowded train station or park? Precision Finding is the best site to Find My Friends. Because to the new, second-generation Ultra Wideband processor, Precision Finding now has three times the range.&nbsp;</p><h2 style=\"margin-bottom: 5px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 20px; line-height: 26px;\"><span style=\"color: inherit; font-family: inherit;\">Buy&nbsp;</span>iPhone 15 Pro 128GB Blue Titanium<span style=\"color: inherit; font-family: inherit;\">&nbsp;from the best Mobile Phone Shop in Bangladesh: Star Tech</span><br></h2><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(1, 19, 45); line-height: 26px;\">In Bangladesh, you can get the original&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Apple iPhone 15 Pro&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">128GB&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Blue Titanium (Singapore)&nbsp;</span>&nbsp;From Star Tech. We have a large collection of the latest&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.startech.com.bd/apple-iphone\" target=\"\" style=\"color: var(--s-primary);\">Apple iPhones</a>&nbsp;to purchase. Order Online Or Visit your Nearest&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.startech.com.bd/\" target=\"\" style=\"color: var(--s-primary);\">Star Tech&nbsp;</a>Shop to get yours at the lowest price.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(1, 19, 45); line-height: 26px;\"><span style=\"background-color: yellow;\">BTRC Approved (One-year Apple warranty all over the world including Bangladesh)</span></p></div>', '2024-05-21 01:58:19', '2024-05-31 09:01:01');
